data.description: Adorable single story home with 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full baths. Recently painted inside, and new carpet installed in the last 8 months. Beautiful mountain views from kitchen, backyard and master bedroom. Vacant and ready for it's new owners!  This home is back on the market at no fault of the sellers. Refrigerator in kitchen, washer and electric dryer, with additional gas dryer in the garage (not hooked up, but matches wash machine) included at no value, or warranty. Also, a swamp cooler is included, no value, or warranty. Pictures do not show appliances, they were taken prior to installation. New security system is included, just have to call to activate service. There is a sprinkler system but it is unknown how long it has not been used.
